  "hash_before": "23be3ed30d7e181521a10df99f53d2572af363ab0c6d57644712e145eaca55cc",
  "heading_path": "热力学第一定律 / 循环过程",
  "intensity": "STRUCTURAL",
  "line_count": 138,
  "masked_text": "[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02998:8fc1fe73dc7c]]\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02999:dd3d144deb56]]\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P03000:e7996bc94720]]\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P03001:ff2eb9e78880]]{solution}\n逆时针循环，该循环中气体对外作的净功为负（也就是外界对气体做功为正），由于内能不变，所以对外放热。\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P03002:06b3847e1b6f]]{solution}\n\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P03003:9bf1d369be09]]\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P03004:ff2eb9e78880]]{solution}\n等压压缩段\n [[PROTECTED:F00001-P03005:1a6cc48c0778]]\n等体升温段\n [[PROTECTED:F00001-P03006:d06775d0e093]]\n等温膨胀段\n [[PROTECTED:F00001-P03007:4a1df0d3e63a]] \n循环净功与效率： 一周后 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P03008:4dd96d0a590a]]，热机吸热发生在 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P03009:6c1ce0ea7cb8]] 和 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P03010:fe18208cb43f]] 两段，所以\n [[PROTECTED:F00001-P03011:2bba90ccdc63]] \n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P03012:06b3847e1b6f]]{solution}\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P03013:3ce271600775]]\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P03014:ff2eb9e78880]]{solution}\n先用 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P03015:b662050878f8]] 求三个状态温度，再逐段使用第一定律。单原子理想气体有 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P03016:e0745766267f]]，且 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P03017:f6726ed83f12]]，因此\n [[PROTECTED:F00001-P03018:dfd64b8d98ac]]\n等体段 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P03019:168cdc66677e]] 不做体积功，等压段 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P03020:6c1ce0ea7cb8]] 可直接用 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P03021:acb1ae333891]]；曲线段 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P03022:fe18208cb43f]] 要先算功，再和内能变化合成热量：\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P03023:f7c731fe7040]]\n循环净功可由三段功相加得到，效率分母只取正吸热量：\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P03024:2795d812e0ba]]\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P03025:06b3847e1b6f]]{solution}\n\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P03026:9ce523ba0f3e]]\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P03027:ff2eb9e78880]]{solution}\n [[PROTECTED:F00001-P03028:37a2d85d81d0]] \n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P03029:229a6ebc2b17]]\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P03030:643cb16d3a59]]\\\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P03031:af543e7d3e57]]\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P03032:06b3847e1b6f]]{solution}\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P03033:1a340fc19952]]\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P03034:ff2eb9e78880]]{solution}\n先把三个状态温度读清楚。设初态为 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P03035:94edd65ca2d0]]，等压膨胀到 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P03036:d114238b8be2]] 时温度变为 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P03037:5bc5a2be7c8e]] \n第二步等体升压到 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P03038:80948b5eddc7]]，此时体积仍为 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P03039:d114238b8be2]]，所以 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P03040:8b205f7bc739]] \n第三步等温膨胀，温度保持 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P03041:7837a744cd1e]]，直到压强回到 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P03042:138523025443]]，于是终态体积为 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P03043:1a0d7a67cd94]]。\n逐段作功。等压段\n [[PROTECTED:F00001-P03044:77606066fa9e]]\n等体段 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P03045:81e6103b988d]] ，等温段\n [[PROTECTED:F00001-P03046:ccb841c71721]]\n故总功为\n [[PROTECTED:F00001-P03047:a92c153d85d0]]\n内能变化由温度决定。理想气体内能只由温度决定：\n [[PROTECTED:F00001-P03048:50d993558443]] \n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P03049:06b3847e1b6f]]{solution}\n",
